    </div> 
    <p>
    As part of my <a href="/research">Masters research</a>, I needed to do a bunch of manipulations to .STL files to generate visualizations of the golfer and club model.  I got frustrated with doing these in high-powered modelling software so I wrote a little python module that reads/writes .STL files and does basic geometric transformations (scaling, rotation, translation).
